										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">水果中含有丰富的维生素每天吃水果补充营养。不过&#8230;&#8230;谈到水果有人欢喜有人忧，有些人吃水果会有反酸胃胀等症状，到底咋回事儿？</span></p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/3a8a6ba1dd922e427f2e1d6968dcc3ad.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">其实，每一种水果的营养成分和药用价值不一样，水果也分寒热凉温，吃的不恰当会得“水果病”。</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/2b78c6b1af102d7e0623e852ff516dbc.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">寒凉类水果</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">主要包括柑、橙、菱角、香蕉、柿子、西瓜等。</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/fead84b37bce82265d7945aa0c0d611b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">温热类水果</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">主要有橘子、枣、栗子、桃、杏、龙眼、荔枝、葡萄、樱桃、石榴、菠萝等。</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/b0bd9e6bb6f077c31e2719228b86ccba.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">甘平类水果</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">主要有李子、椰子、枇杷、山楂、苹果等。</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/0ecd8d0e71e8932e40acfb38cfb9f3f5.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">荔枝病-头晕乏力</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/c169f5567709c8e4e6aa6ec11d078475.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">若出现上述症状，应立刻停止食用荔枝，喝糖水休息片刻即可缓解。</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/788021b6abd70b7c3f80c76c2f4d98c0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">健康吃法:</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">适量食用，每次尽量不超过2两，试着对照自己的拳头，大约一个拳头的大小。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">温馨提醒：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">荔枝不可过量食用，亦不可空腹食用，较合适的食用时间是饭后半小时。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">在吃荔枝前后可适当喝点绿茶、绿豆汤，也可把新鲜荔枝去皮浸入淡盐水中，放入冰柜里冷藏后食用。这样不仅可以防止上火，还有醒脾消食的作用。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">榴莲病-脸上冒痘痘</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">榴莲被誉为 “水果之王”，营养丰富；但也并非人人适宜，尤其是阴虚体质的人群不宜多吃。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">不适反应：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">榴莲中脂肪含量为4.1%，是所有水果中含量最高的。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">榴莲性热，吃过量容易导致脸上的痤疮加剧，并且会导致口干舌燥，甚至还会引发流鼻血。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">健康吃法：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">吃榴莲避免上火的方法除了适量食用外，还可以和山竹搭配食用，因为山竹性偏寒凉可以清热“败火”。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">李子病-酸倒脾胃</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">李子酸酸甜甜的口感，相信有不少人喜欢。每年到了李子成熟的季节，“爱李之人”就会大量吃李子，这易导致胃部不适。</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/08807cedf7bb2e15ad13e393c2778b3b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">不适反应：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">成熟的李子有促消化、增加食欲的功效。但李子果酸含量高，吃过多易伤脾胃，引起腹胀等现象，尤其儿童更不宜一次性吃太多。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">未成熟的李子尽量不吃，会有中毒的可能性。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">健康吃法：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">建议一次性不可食用太多。或者可以加点冰糖一起炖，做成酸甜的糖水，有一定的润喉利嗓作用。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">温馨提醒：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">犹如李子、杨梅等口感特别酸的水果都会有上述同样的不适反应，吃的时候需注意量。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">芒果病-吃完嘴边痒</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/80fb7ce1177ed000ddbc617cb95cb5c0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/ea8cf8eb546b1233e2f37f1b1a5a9ba7.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">以上所举的例子中</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">有的不是当季水果食用群体较少</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">出现问题率较低</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">但也不可忽略哦</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">接下来，小编要和大家聊聊</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">这个季节适合吃的应季水果和食物</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">1、苹果</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1b67565aece61b337a8f8465006100b4.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/423bfe85075eaa04c6574774afd45115.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/7c6d1e5b001499343a402e4ab3b5c75a.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2、梨</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/4bda00894bfff7665b409425b9469548.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/a5fdef961ed5f653461cdadf81dc30a1.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/9838643d3000aba626caa71cf26d9c16.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3、板栗</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/0a1d793ea392e018c8b8c08df6329438.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/097f79fb983ae71964b688e02ea2a65d.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/fda9205f0814566e9ff3d1c20b6eba72.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">4、甘蔗</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/b7e0f846ad41936c3e4e69e9f63d69ab.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/c36fd03720a21f5782d484064a49c1b1.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/d5bd262da4dfeb663e458af44c7b8c54.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">5、荸荠</p><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/e19a4889a80c15a5182b087cb99de15a.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/cb7e8f0b7c7aa2f2339adc360ed69da8.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/49e77e713620a0707dc7e1813dfabb33.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
